==English==

===Etymology===
From [[haptonema]], a peg-like structure of unknown function that is present in the members.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[hapto-|hapto]][[-phyte|phyte]]}}

#{{cattag|Botany}} A kind of [[unicellular]] [[marine]] [[phytoplankton]], typically covered in tiny [[scale]]s or [[plate]]s composed of [[carbohydrate]]s and [[calcium]] deposits.

====Synonyms====
*[[coccolithophore]]
*[[coccolithophorid]]
*[[Haptophyta]]
*[[Prymnesiophyta]]

